name: Dating Frank and Jamal
description:
A complete visual novel made using scratch. Enjoy beautiful premade art by the scratch team and royalty free music. Featuring unique one dimensional characters, experience all the highs and lows of teenage love in this semi-engaging visual novel. With 5 possible outcomes, who knows where your story will take you? Will you find true love or will it remain unrequited? Can you get all 5 endings? (Of course you can they are very easy to get) It’s up to you!
